                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-66-off395 t18080113-66-cd396"></join>, twenty four whisk brooms, value 16 s. fourteen broom sticks, value 1 s. seven leather bands, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080113-66-victim698" type="victimName">
